      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels brand new without the showroom price tag? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s in spectacular shape! This car has been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, meticulously cleaned, and it still has that fresh car smell. It\u2019s seriously flawless, inside and out. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I know the next owner is going to fall in love the second they sit behind the wheel. Come swing by and see it for yourself\u2014you definitely won't be disappointed!",
