    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior features a flawless factory finish with deep, mirror-like clarity, completely free of stone chips, door dings, or scratches. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium Nappa leather remains supple and matte, showing no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the original protective films are still present on several trim pieces. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been maintained exclusively at the dealership with a comprehensive folder of service records included. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover, never driven in inclement weather, and remains 100% stock. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key example that satisfies even the most discerning inspection. Includes both original keys, all owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker.",
      "price": 46500.0,
